   &trans          &kp COMMA  &kp S     &ru_o  &ru_u  &kp EXCL                   &kp LS(N7)  &kp K  &kp L  &ru_w  &ru_z  &trans
   &trans          &kp W      &ru_i     &ru_e  &kp F  &kp FSLH                   &kp D       &kp X  &kp N  &kp C  &kp Y  &kp Z
   &trans          &kp U      &kp LBKT  &ru_j  &kp R  &kp LS(FSLH)               &ru_hash    &kp H  &kp V  &kp A  &kp G  &trans

                            &trans  &trans  &hold_sym_r 0 SPACE                  &trans  &trans  &trans
                        >;
