                                 ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░│░░░░░░░│      │       │░ ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░
                                                 └───────┘      └───────┘░
                                                                 ░░░░░░░░░

Mnemonics — a symbol sits on the key whose EN-logical letter cues it:
  _  on U (underscore)    =  on E (equals)      `  on G (grave)
  \  on B (backslash)     -  on D (dash)        ~  on T (tilde)
  $  on S (dollar)        %  on P (percent)     *  on X (times / x)
  #  on N (number)
Positional: ':' sits left of '.', and ';' sits left of ','.
Brackets: openers on the left hand, closers mirrored on the right.
Inner columns (! . , ? #) are the always-on punctuation shared with the base layers.
*/

                        bindings = <
   &bt BT_CLR    &kp BSLH   &kp LPAR   &kp LBKT  &kp UNDER  &kp EXCL             &kp QMARK  &kp RPAR   &kp MINUS  &kp RBKT   &kp AMPS   &bt BT_SEL 2
   &bt BT_SEL 0  &kp LBRC   &kp LT     &kp EQUAL &kp COLON  &kp DOT              &kp RBRC   &kp GT     &kp TILDE  &kp DLLR   &kp PLUS   &bt BT_SEL 3
   &bt BT_SEL 1  &kp GRAVE  &kp STAR   &kp AT    &kp SEMI   &kp COMMA            &kp HASH   &kp DQT    &kp APOS   &kp FSLH   &kp PRCNT  &bt BT_SEL 4

                                     &none &none &none                        &kp RET &none &studio_unlock
                        >;
                };






